improved_metadata.title: Ink & Cotton Empire
improved_metadata.description: This song is a raw depiction of the hustle and artistry involved in screen printing, from the late nights to the burns and the ambition to build an empire. It blends the grit of the streets with the precision of design.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Sweat and ink, that's my Cologne building, empire's out of polyester and cotton
